00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:20,030
but I can't drink coffee on an empty stomach.

282
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:22,500
Then don't.

283
00:19:31,610 --> 00:19:33,710
We'll just fill up our stomachs with coffee.

284
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:36,340
