Not 911?

291
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:04,150
I think the roads are still stuck, 
since 911 is doing it like that.

292
00:20:04,150 --> 00:20:06,340
Nurse Ohn, take that kid to the tent.

293
00:20:06,340 --> 00:20:07,700
Yes.

294
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:14,760
We're here.

295
