00:45:05,040 --> 00:45:08,240
Nice. 
-Thank you.

626
00:45:25,260 --> 00:45:27,610
You...that-

627
00:45:54,360 --> 00:45:57,350
Now I think I'll live.

628
00:45:57,350 --> 00:46:00,840
Sugar's the best for recharging.

629
00:46:04,720 --> 00:46:07,550
Doctor.

