I don't have intentions to end it.

721
00:54:29,920 --> 00:54:31,830
Park Ji Na.

722
00:54:35,050 --> 00:54:37,420
You said manners?

723
00:54:38,370 --> 00:54:43,240
We've been living apart for 20 years, but we were still family once.

